what_you_do: Milana Leshinsky helps passionate coaches turn their expertise into a beautifully simple, scalable business—through group programs, signature offers, and aligned marketing.
social_proof: Milana is the author of two books, "Coaching Millions" and "Simplicity Entrepreneurship", and the creator of Coaching Genie, an online platform for designing and delivering coaching programs.
business_focus: Helping coaches create easy-to-scale coaching programs and overcome fear of technology.
